<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Quebec_French&amp;action=edit&amp;section=44" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="References_2">References</span></h2>
<div class="reflist" style="list-style-type: decimal;"></div>
